<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA44">
<l>ulakamu mūḻiyu māḻiyu moṇkē</l>
<l>ḻalarkatiruñ centīyu māvāṉ – palakatirkaḷ</l>
<l>pāritta paimpoṉ muṭiyā ṉaṭiyiṇaikkē</l>
<l>pūritteṉ ṉeñcē puri</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>By the two feet of him with the green-golden  crown</l>
<l>that spreads many rays, of him who is the world, the aeons,</l> 
<l>the ocean, the [sun] rays expanding with bright lustre, and red fire,</l>
<l>be filled, my heart, [and] desire [them].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
